%h1 Components

%p Components are the main building blocks of the language.

%p Components have the following features:

%ul
  %li
    they can be composed inside each other

  %li
    they can be connected to
    %b stores

  %li
    they can subscribe to
    %b providers

  %li
    styles can be defined for HTML elements inside them

  %li
    properties can be defined with types and default values
